{"tid":630454,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇啲結局峰迴路轉/燒腦細胞既戲令你好難忘？","createTime":"2018-04-15T15:25:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-20T04:05:43.000Z","uid":156018,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"cc39a995bdab6134744fed34b4e910c65171215b","tid":630454,"uid":156018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T15:25:36.000Z","msg":"最近迷上左呢類「燒腦電影」初初睇左幾套經典既都覺得好精彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 拋啲磚仔出黎想求巴絲們其他強力推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n（盡量無劇透）<br />\n1.  Triangle，無限loop經典之一，一個老母為左返屋企救個仔而loop<br />\n2. MEMENTO記憶碎片，男主有短暫失憶症，靠相同紋身去記低周遭事物，劇情不斷左穿右插，到最後全部整合埋一齊個下好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n3. Identity，應該都算係燒腦界癲峰作品，講男主同一班人係旅館遇到殺人事件，每個人都跟住順序咁死<br />\n4. 神探，主演劉青雲，佢係一個可以睇到人地心魔既偵探，第一次睇換槍果段真係黑人問號"},{"pid":"ed6f1c4521cf44cba6483f595059fa50c0aa24ee","tid":630454,"uid":47948,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T15:28:10.000Z","msg":"seven pounds<br />\nthe prestige"},{"pid":"cb95a51722171763d555b07f628d6747e3528d44","tid":630454,"uid":156018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T01:21:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c59b4fb9324fbf027b522ce991a4463d23cae8e9","tid":630454,"uid":156018,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T06:21:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d23700cc649820538f3c921f791c3f72638fd605","tid":630454,"uid":12468,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T06:22:43.000Z","msg":"盡量無劇透但都係劇透左"},{"pid":"a9f2432e886ff0341b5a5f99ef9681c40904892b","tid":630454,"uid":19528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"